Mind Blow #96 developed at Harvard but this

00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:48.740
new Exo-Glove from Seoul National University
is more compact and more comfortable.

00:03:48.740 --> 00:03:54.020
The flexible, waterproof polymer soft robot
is tendon driven using actuators and allows

00:03:54.020 --> 00:03:58.080
